Package sdds.lab2.task2

Class TransactionRecord

java.lang.Object
sdds.lab2.task2.TransactionRecord
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TransactionRecord extends Object implements Serializable
TransactionRecord class holds data, that is stored inside the transaction file for each account for a given period. It defines 2 constructors and getter setter methods for all the attributes in this class.
Since:
08/02/2022
Version:
